article:
'Smithville' is the name of some places in the United States of America:
*Smithville, former name of Loomis, California *Smithville, Georgia *Smithville,
Monroe County, Indiana *Smithville, Owen County, Indiana *Smithville,
Mississippi *Smithville, Missouri *Smithville, New Jersey (disambiguation),
multiple locations *Smithville, New York *Smithville, Ohio *Smithville, Rhode
Island *Smithville, Tennessee *Smithville, Texas *Smithville, West Virginia
*Smithville, Arkansas *Surry, Virginia, former name

'Smithville' is also the name of two settlements in Canada: *Smithville, Nova
Scotia *Smithville, Ontario

[[Smithville (album)]] is also the name of an album by jazz musician Louis Smith
